<meta name="description" content="Fudo (Fudou) Myo-o. Skt. = Acala. The commander of the Wisdom Kings or Mantra Kings. Deity of Esoteric (Tantric) Buddhism in Japan. Emination of Dainichi Buddha. Buddha Statues of Japan.">

